Jonathan Jaffe


										Corporate Finance									

										Dental & Opthamology Practices									

jonathan@ahcteam.com
After graduating from Fordham Law School, Jonathan Jaffe entered the investment banking world by specializing in corporate finance and Mergers & Acquisitions with a special emphasis in the sale of national dental practices and finance. He has been an investment advisor at several large firms, including J.P. Morgan and Credit Suisse. Today, Mr. Jaffe oversees all loan production at AHC from his San Francisco office, processing over $100 Million in loan applications yearly for Term Loans, Accounts Receivable Loans, SBA Loans and Mezzanine financing. He also maintains a strong presence in Dental M&A transactions. 







Kathrine Eldridge, D.D.S.


