For over 17 years, prior to embarking on a career in Healthcare Investments, Sam Bludyan was an entrepreneur and business owner. Having vast experience as a principal and proprietor of healthcare related enterprises, Sam is uniquely positioned to identify current business trends and to effectively evaluate healthcare opportunities. His refreshing style and comfort with taking on even the most difficult challenges make Sam an outstanding advocate for his clients, whether they are buyers or sellers of Healthcare Opportunities.







John Nugent


